
           =-=-=-=-=-=-=-=- Hill Giant  -=-=-=-=-=-=

    Hill Giants are huge, muscular men standing twice the height
of men.  They possess immense strength and are not very agile.
They are also not very smart and therefore only good for fighting.


SUMMARY:

Dex: Low               Str: Very high        Con: Very high 
Int: Below Avg         Wis: Low              Char: Low

HP Regen: Above Avg
SP Regen: Nil
Natural Weaponry/Damage: Standard (High)
Natural Armour: Tough Skin (Above Avg)
Ambidextry: Nil
Innate spells/skills: Nil
Exp Modifier: Below Avg

